STEVENS et al., Appellants, v. ANDREAS, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. March 5, 1894.) Appeal from judgment on report of referee. Action by Frank A. Stevens and another against Maria W. Andreas;

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BISOHOPP and PRYOR, JJ.

J. Larkin, for appellants. Morse & Wensley, for respondent

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal for nonservice of printed- papers-granted.
